  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a developer, I want to be able to submit  pending senttransactions with a different gas price or gas limit and same nonce **so that** I can speed up transactions, unclog a clogged transaction queue, prevent the failed execution of a transaction with too low gas limit, etc.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Summary*:\r\n* extra option appearing in Transaction history for pending sent transactions, in-line (no need to go to Transaction details to find it)\r\n* extra option: a small button with \"Speed up\"\r\n* the name is simplified for UX, it actually lets you tweak both gas price and gas limit, and in both directions\r\n* nice-to-have, but not critical: give gas price estimates (a la Metamask)\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nSee above",
